quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  36,37,"Àmì kan ni òru jẹ́ fún wọn, tí À ń yọ ọ̀sán jáde láti inú rẹ̀. Nígbà náà (tí A bá yọ ọ́ tán) wọn yóò tún wà nínú òkùnkùn (alẹ́ mìíràn).1 {1}",footnotes:1:Kókó inú āyah yìí ni pé, òru l’ó ń ṣíwájú ọ̀sán nínú ọjọ́, bí àpẹ̀ẹrẹ, òru Jímọ̀ mọ́júmọ́ ọ̀sán Jímọ̀, òru Sabt mọ́júmọ́ ọ̀sán Sabt. Nítorí náà, kò sí òru Àlàmísì mọ́júmọ́ ọ̀sán Jímọ̀. Kò sì sí òru Jímọ̀ mọ́júmọ́ Sabt.
  36,38,"Àti pé òòrùn yóò máa rìn lọ sí àyè rẹ̀. Ìyẹn ni ètò (ti) Alágbára, Onímọ̀."
  36,39,"Òṣùpá náà, A ti ṣe òdíwọ̀n àwọn ibùsọ̀ fún un (tí ó ti ma máa tóbi sí i) títí ó máa fi padà dà bíi àran ọ̀pẹ tó ti pẹ́ (gbígbẹ)."
  37,22,"Ẹ kó àwọn tó ṣàbòsí jọ, àwọn ìyàwó wọn àti ohun tí wọ́n ń jọ́sìn fún"
  37,23,"lẹ́yìn Allāhu. Kí ẹ sì júwe wọn sí ojú ọ̀nà iná Jẹhīm."
  37,24,"Ẹ dá wọn dúró ná, dájúdájú wọ́n máa bi wọ́n léèrè ìbéèrè."
  38,1,"Sọ̄d. (Allāhu ló mọ ohun tí Ó gbàlérò pẹ̀lú háràfí náà.)Allāhu fi al-Ƙur’ān tí ó kún fún ìrántí bura. {1}",footnotes:1:Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al Baƙọrah;  2:1.
  38,2,"Síbẹ̀síbẹ̀ àwọn tó ṣàì gbàgbọ́ wà nínú ìgbéraga àti ìyapa (òdodo)."
  38,3,"Mélòó mélòó nínú àwọn ìran tí A ti parẹ́ ṣíwájú wọn. Nígbà náà, wọ́n kígbe (fún ìrànlọ́wọ́) nígbà tí kò sí ibùsásí kan."